1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,712
When the creature falls... silence returns to the tomb.

2
00:00:04,712 --> 00:00:09,246
And then, from the ancient stone... a spirit appears.

3
00:00:09,246 --> 00:00:16,270
Tristan — the hero who gave his life to seal the Balrog — reaches out his hand.

4
00:00:16,270 --> 00:00:18,227
He offers no guidance.

5
00:00:18,227 --> 00:00:19,027
No power.

6
00:00:19,027 --> 00:00:20,360
No explanation.

7
00:00:20,360 --> 00:00:22,850
Only a title... his successor.

8
00:00:22,850 --> 00:00:27,829
The one who prevented the revival, even once... is enough.

9
00:00:27,829 --> 00:00:39,832
It is a recognition born of desperation — a dead hero... passing his burden to a stranger... because there is no one else left to carry it.
